        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Kosalans in a certain forest grove. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa catuddasa balībaddā naṭṭhā honti. ",
          "en": "Now at that time one of the brahmins of the Bhāradvāja clan had lost fourteen oxen. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo te balībadde gavesanto yena so vanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā addasa bhagavantaṃ tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. ",
          "en": "While looking for them he went to that forest, where he saw the Buddha sitting down cross-legged, with his body straight, and mindfulness established right there. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:1.4",
          "pli": "Disvāna yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
          "en": "He went up to the Buddha, and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:2.1",
          "pli": "“Na hi nūnimassa samaṇassa, ",
          "en": "“This ascetic mustn’t have "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:2.2",
          "pli": "Balībaddā catuddasa; ",
          "en": "fourteen oxen "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:2.3",
          "pli": "Ajjasaṭṭhiṃ na dissanti, ",
          "en": "missing for the past six days: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:2.4",
          "pli": "Tenāyaṃ samaṇo sukhī. ",
          "en": "that’s why this ascetic is happy. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:3.1",
          "pli": "Na hi nūnimassa samaṇassa, ",
          "en": "This ascetic mustn’t have "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:3.2",
          "pli": "Tilākhettasmi pāpakā; ",
          "en": "a field of sesame ruined, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:3.3",
          "pli": "Ekapaṇṇā dupaṇṇā ca, ",
          "en": "with just one or two leaves: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:3.4",
          "pli": "Tenāyaṃ samaṇo sukhī. ",
          "en": "that’s why this ascetic is happy. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:4.1",
          "pli": "Na hi nūnimassa samaṇassa, ",
          "en": "This ascetic mustn’t have "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:4.2",
          "pli": "Tucchakoṭṭhasmi mūsikā; ",
          "en": "rats in a vacant barn "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:4.3",
          "pli": "Ussoḷhikāya naccanti, ",
          "en": "dancing merrily: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.10:4.4",
          "pli": "Tenāyaṃ samaṇo sukhī. ",
          "en": "that’s why this ascetic is happy. "
        },
        {
